    62792 [label="HitachiOpenLicense:\nThe author is the person or entity providing the software under this license.\nSource code refers to the source code and configuration files used to create the\nexecutable. The term \"executable\" refers to the executables, binary files and\nconfiguration and data files required for the software to be included in the\nsoftware. The term \"article\" refers to any article by the author describing how\na user might use the source code or executable of the software. The publisher is\nthe provider of the software's media, such as websites, magazines, CD-ROMs and\nDVDs."
